troubleshooting
---------------------------- document_id ----------------------------
2856
---------------------------- title ----------------------------
Error starting application server with the Java agent
---------------------------- permalink ----------------------------
error-starting-application-server-with-the-java-agent
---------------------------- keywords ----------------------------
java agent library failed init instrument zip opening
---------------------------- body ----------------------------
The path to the agent jar file must be fully qualified in the -javaagent JVM switch.  If the path is not correctly specified, this error will be thrown on application server startup and the JVM will exit:

    Error opening zip file: newrelic.jar
    Error occurred during initialization of VM
    agent library failed to init: instrument

To correct the issue, specify the full path to the newrelic.jar file in the -javaagent switch.  For example, if the newrelic.jar file is in a directory named newrelic inside the Tomcat home directory /home/tomcat, the switch should be specified as follows:

`-javaagent:/home/tomcat/newrelic/newrelic.jar`
